<br>
Ah am at present 52nd seasons an a Cleric o Blessed Brell<br>
<br>
Therefore Ah am of Good alignment an follow tha strictly - Ah frown on those tha think tha they can bend to darkness an still follow t' light.<br>
<br>
Be honorable in all aspects o yer life. Fight wit honor. Bow not to darkness. Help those tha are young. When ye duel do so wit compassion. Seek not to hurry through life - money is not the answer to everything but only a step along t' way. Seek ye wisdom therefore look around before ye run foreward.<br>
<br>
(ooc) Seeking the highest level in a hurry is a poor way to play - and money grubbing is bad gaming. Dueling without fair play is poor sportsmanship - rez, heal and buff the other after - Offer congratulations on winning or losing. Insulting with good jibes is RP - calling names is not.<br>
<br>
Invading is ok - Training and blocking exits is bad play and should not be done. If upset stop and leave.<br>
<br>
This is a game -- REMEMBER THAT -- ENJOY IT (We all forget that sometimes).<br>
<br>
